replies.body:
I can't speak for naut, but as for Sejuani. If you are blue, start krugs (get a leas and don't smite) then go red buff (smite it) then go dragon crab, then frog (smite) then blue and from there either recall or clear wolves depending on your health. Get {{item:3713}} {{item:1001}} and 4x{{item:2003}} 

If you want an early gank, it has to be a lvl 2 gank using your summoner as gap closer (flash or ghost will do the trick) usually mid is a good place.

If you are purple. Then you start frog (smite) blue, dragon crab, wolves recall and then do red side
